# VEHICLE::SET_VEHICLE_ENGINE_CAN_DEGRADE

## Summary
Enable/disable the aircraft engine degrade

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle: Index - Index of the vehicle.
* **BOOL** enableDegrading: Enable/disable engine degrading
